high_descs: Turn around and got to left side of the refrigerator to the black container in the floor.
Remove the apple from the inside of the container.
Turn to your right and head to the microwave on the counter on the other side of the room.
Place the apple inside of the microwave on the plate and heat it, remove it when done.
Turn back around and head back to the container on the left side of the refrigerator.
Place the apple back into the black container.
anns.task_desc: Take a apple and heat it put it back when finished.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the fridge, turn left again and walk up to the small black bin to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the apple out of the small black bin.
Turn around and forward, then hang a left and walk across the room to the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and put the apple inside then close the door, turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave and remove the now heated apple, then close the microwave.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk across the room to the fridge.
Put the heated apple in the small black bin to the left of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in a black bin.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the trash can next to the fridge.
Pick up the apple from the trash can.
Make a right to walk to the microwave.
Heat up the apple in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn around and make a right to walk back to the trash can next to the fridge.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Heat up an apple from the trash can in the microwave to put it back.
